# Game server URL for native apps (Expo Go / dev builds).
# - Web dev ignores this and uses the Metro proxy automatically.
# - Native dev with Railway/ngrok: set a public https URL — it takes priority over LAN.
# - Native dev with local server: use localhost or omit; Expo LAN host is used automatically.
#
# Railway example:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_SERVER_URL=https://your-service.up.railway.app
EXPO_PUBLIC_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:4000
